track.name: Call It Stormy Monday
comments: This band is great.  Professional musicians of the highest caliber.
The Eagle flies on Friday,Saturday I go out to play......
They knew how to do it back then, good.
There are no bad versions of stormy monday but like smoke some are a lot better than others.  T-Bone is Maui Wowwy
rember the apple       women cant  live with  them cant live without them
Testify Mr. T-Bone Walker to me!...you brought it first!

There are so many versions by T Bone and so many covers that it becomes tedious to hear people arguing over who's is the best. Check out the rhythm guitar stuttering in the background on this - genius even before he starts that trademark soloing...
The Allman Brothers At Fillmore East version will blow you away.
